===== Action =====

This class is designed to work with actions. 

Object references: \\
  * [[manual:api:reference:action:object#action|Action]]
  * [[manual:api:reference:action:object#action_condition|Action condition]]
  * [[manual:api:reference:action:object#action_operation|Action operation]]

Available methods: \\

  * ''[[manual:api:reference:action:create|action.create]]'' - create new actions
  * ''[[manual:api:reference:action:delete|action.delete]]'' - delete actions
  * ''[[manual:api:reference:action:get|action.get]]'' - retrieve actions
  * ''[[manual:api:reference:action:update|action.update]]'' - update actions
